FAURIA PLANS TO ATTEND NORTHERN ARIZONA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Quinn Fauria of Crespi High, a Times' All-Valley defensive lineman, said 
Thursday that he has verbally committed to attend Northern Arizona, a Division 
I-AA school in the Big Sky Conference. 
</P>
