<P>
Photo, Christian's Tiffany Stutz says she's surprised by her early success, but 
her coach isn't. BARBARA MARTIN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Alex Davis is only 
15, but his size and maturity have made him one of Hoover's team leaders. BOB 
GRIESER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
