JAPAN -- FOREIGN POLICY; TAKESHITA, NOBORU; UNITED STATES -- BUDGET; FEDERAL 
DEFICIT; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; JAPAN -- FOREIGN AID 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
