APPOINTMENTS; UNITED STATES -- AMBASSADORS; NEGROPONTE, JOHN D; NICARAGUA -- 
REVOLTS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN AID -- NICARAGUA; GUERRILLAS -- NICARAGUA 
</P>
