 TRAILERS OFFERED TO CITY FOR HOMELESS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Santa Monica may receive 10 trailers to serve as shelters for homeless people 
-- if officials can find a place to park them. 
</P>
