UNIONS; MEDICAL CARE -- LOS ANGELES; HOME HEALTH CARE; CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT 
EMPLOYEES -- WAGES AND SALARIES; HOMECARE WORKERS -- LABOR RELATIONS 
</P>
